<plot>A troubled, orphaned teenager living in a boy's home seeks comfort in a corrido his deceased grandfather taught him as a child. Finding it increasingly difficult to play the corrido in the environment he lives in, Tomas ventures on a journey back to his grandfather's old rural house. In the old and dilapidated house, Tomas finds much more than the long forgotten artifacts of his childhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?496315</url></doc>
